<Base title="Pipedrive Integrations — DH7" description="Custom integrations for Pipedrive. Keep your CRM in sync with the rest of your business in real time.">
  <h1>Pipedrive Integrations</h1>

  <p>Pipedrive is a strong sales CRM. But sales data doesn't live in isolation — it needs to connect to the tools your operations, finance, and logistics teams rely on.</p>

  <p>We build integrations that keep Pipedrive in sync with the rest of your business.</p>

  <h2>Deals and pipeline</h2>

  <p>When a deal moves in Pipedrive, other systems should know. We can sync deal stage changes to your operations platform, trigger fulfilment workflows, or update a shared status board — without anyone manually bridging the gap.</p>

  <h2>Contacts and organisations</h2>

  <p>Contacts created in Pipedrive can flow to your other systems automatically. Changes made elsewhere — a new billing contact, an updated address — can flow back in. No duplicate entry, no stale data.</p>

  <h2>Activities and follow-ups</h2>

  <p>We can route Pipedrive activities and notes to communication tools like Slack or Teams, so the right people are informed at the right time without needing to log into the CRM.</p>

  <h2>Real-time</h2>

  <p>Pipedrive's webhook API means integrations don't need to poll. Changes are pushed as they happen, so downstream systems are updated in seconds.</p>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Tell us what you're trying to connect. We'll tell you what's possible.</p>
  <p><a href="mailto:damien@26brains.com">damien@26brains.com</a></p>
</Base>
